               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I helped to unload Mr. Whitaker's cart that morn<lb></lb>ing—he went round the market, and when he came back I was gone, and he charged me with the robbery—it is false about my going for the coat.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MRS. WALTHO</hi>. I swear he is the man.</p>
